# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================

# This .gitignore is designed for maximum security:
# 1. Vault passwords are NEVER committed
# 2. Actual config files are ignored (only .example versions are tracked)
# 3. Encrypted vault.yml files ARE safe to commit
# 4. SSH keys and certificates are excluded
# 5. Log files and temporary files are excluded
#
# Always verify before committing:
#   git status
#   git diff --cached
#
# To check what would be committed:
#   git add . --dry-run
